    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    FunctionGenerationStrategy
    The FunctionGenerationStrategy interface defines the contract for generating functions using an external service or logic.
    FunctionGenerator<I,O>
    Represents a function created from natural language prompts, test scenarios, or test classes.
    FunctionGenerator.Builder<I,O>
    A builder for creating generated functions using descriptions, scenarios, test classes, or custom strategies.
    LlamaFunctionGenerator
    The LlamaFunctionGenerator class is responsible for generating functions using the Llama API.
    LlamaFunctionGenerator.Builder
    Builder class for constructing a LlamaFunctionGenerator.
    OpenAIFunctionGenerator
    The OpenAIFunctionGenerator class is responsible for generating functions using the OpenAI API.
    OpenAIFunctionGenerator.Builder
    Builder class for constructing an OpenAIFunctionGenerator.
    Scenario<I,O>
    Represents an input-output scenario for a generated function.
